
'''* Ph.D. Thesis: Incorporating the Commons: A Political Economic Analysis of Corporate Involvement in Free and Open Source Software. Benjamin Birkinbine. School of Journalism and Communicationand the Graduate School of the University of Oregon, September 2014'''

